<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-08-18T16:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-08-18T16:00:00-05:00" n="219" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d219">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72119/737a</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                    to the <gloss type="to">Diplomatic Representatives in Allied
                                        Countries</gloss>
                                </hi><note n="1" xml:id="d219fn1">Also to the Chargé in Siam, the
                                    Chargé in Rumania, and the Special Agent in Corfu, Aug. 20, 4
                                    p.m. (File No. 763.72119/742a.)</note>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Circular telegram]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-08-18T16:00:00-05:00">
                                        <hi rend="italic">August 18, 1917, 4 p.m.</hi>
                                    </date>
                                </dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>Please ascertain as promptly as possible the views of the Government
                                to which you are accredited in regard to the Pope’s recent peace
                                communication. The above information is desired by the President.
                                Cable reply, which will be treated as strictly confidential.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <persName corresp="#p_LR1">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                                    </persName>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>